{"tid":2430882,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺根本就冇中國人哩個Term?","createTime":"2021-03-03T08:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T13:58:31.000Z","uid":18521,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a6d0b85817b3713e3234483a802ab6a0199679","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:46:20.000Z","msg":"點解台灣人唔可以係正式中國人? <br />\n點解香港人唔可以係正式中國人? <br />\n點解得中共國D人先可以叫中國人?<br />\n究竟何謂「中國」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣改名做「中正國」又可以叫中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本改名做「中心國」又可以叫中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本「中國」哩個Term由頭到尾只係一個名 因為起個名叫「中華人民共和國」所以就叫中國<br />\n如果個名係「蘇維埃中華共和國」(真係以前中共國既名) 就叫蘇國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果個名係「美麗的中國」就叫美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係清朝就叫清國，根本上就無所謂中唔中國人<br />\n<br />\n清朝人都唔會覺得明朝人係自己一份子啦，因為大家根本係唔同國家既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反清復明既人會認為係復興緊自己國家，因為唔覺得清朝係自己國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「中國」哩個Term實際上只係近代民國先出現既說法，一種激化/團結民族主義既手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Chinese&quot; 係應該譯做「華人/華裔」，因為事實上可以分為 &quot;ethically Chinese&quot; 同 &quot;nationally Chinese&quot;，而哩個世界的確係有好多人只係 &quot;ethically Chinese&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n中國哩塊土地確實係有好多歷史同文化，但唔係「中國」既歷史，係華人既歷史同文化。<br />\n我地可以因為身為「華人」或繼承「華人文化」而自豪，但唔會係因為「中國人」而自豪<br />\n台灣人亦有好好保存以往中國哩片土地既歷史係台灣既故宮，博物館，因為哩D的確係華人既歷史文化。<br />\n<br />\n所以下次有人問你「你係咪中國人」，可以問返佢究竟咩叫中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫佢自己思考一下"},{"pid":"29546c2d3e01003002a5edf7e418a1b2c201fed1","tid":2430882,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人哋理撚得你班清倉"},{"pid":"702afb79d46d0d5d50b3b7e27f2b9100add60337","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29546c2d3e01003002a5edf7e418a1b2c201fed1","tid":2430882,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人哋理撚得你班清倉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"我一向認為唔應該激化種族主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c6c4f7cd184ce05bebf76130e89f27ae462b90","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"我最後既意思係當D廢老咁問你既時候可以咁答<br />\n但鬼佬既話可以直接了當D答香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fab82bfef7ddc3fa55e527ed6ffb2bbdfe8e23","tid":2430882,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:53:31.000Z","msg":"黃皮膚黑頭髮吖親<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kq8AgNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkq8AgNs.jpg&h=f36e7227&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bce7d19a945970eb94613b10bcb1a4ce17bece81","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f8ac5420e908d97b1d3e565a66a2913405beb2","tid":2430882,"uid":22535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:10:52.000Z","msg":"只有支那共匪佔領區"},{"pid":"15bd6ea70ae1ece7d7cfbc1b4126f79637ebd10d","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5434f3aa