me":"2021-03-03T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無腦嘅人無得拗"},{"pid":"c803d2d0a0a5c9c43670f2bcdfb4604685cca806","tid":2430882,"uid":359755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"咩Ethically<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Ethnically下話<br />\n意思差好遠喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dd8c7ef9b583deaa77b3ada07771f337b8c407","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c803d2d0a0a5c9c43670f2bcdfb4604685cca806","tid":2430882,"uid":359755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"咩Ethically<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Ethnically下話<br />\n意思差好遠喎ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:10:04.000Z","msg":"Sorr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />串錯左字"},{"pid":"d47d0182823516a6d4fae753db6e16b2a27c687f","tid":2430882,"uid":48222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"「中國」一詞已經被共匪騎劫咗，佢特登運用中文本身「曖昧不明」嘅文字特性去隨意搬龍門去達成自己嘅統戰目標"},{"pid":"c1856d833c66cba645c0b5150936ae5b300b9d29","tid":2430882,"uid":180418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"小學己經有教中國係代表中心之國，幾撚自大，所有野圍住佢轉"},{"pid":"4191b64d539e9f312dd09fcbfe26eb935cbac2fa","tid":2430882,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1856d833c66cba645c0b5150936ae5b300b9d29","tid":2430882,"uid":180418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"小學己經有教中國係代表中心之國，幾撚自大，所有野圍住佢轉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T13:58:31.000Z","msg":"唔知哩個說法嘅來源到底係來自邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.